enemy1.name: Thanos
enemy1.strengths: Super Strength, invulnerability, immortality, telepathy, teleportation, genius intellect, force fields, matter manipulation, and energy projection
enemy1.weaknesses: Perhaps the closest thing to a weakness that Thanos has is that every time he transcends to godhood and takes over the universe (Cosmic Cube, Infinity Gauntlet, Heart of the Universe), he feels unworthy to wield such powers, and intentionally orchestrates his own downfall such that he is no longer omnipotent.

enemy2.name: Ronan the Accuser
enemy2.strengths: Superhuman strength, superehuman durability, enhanced agility, and regenerative healing
enemy2.weaknesses: His hammer that carries the Power Stone is his only weakness

enemy3.name: Korath the Pursuer
enemy3.strengths: Superhuman strength, superhuman durability, enhanced agility, and regenerative healing factor
enemy3.weaknesses: Being killed by Drax the Destroyer

enemy4.name: Ego
enemy4.strengths: Energy manipulation, light tentacles, light beams, light form, power drawing, hypnosis inducement, biological manipulation: self healing, shapeshifting, superhuman strength, superhuman durability, immortality, matter manipulation, flight, planetary form, and seedling creation

enemy5.name: Abilisk
enemy5.strengths: Thick hide, super strength, super durability, matter waves, amd interdimensional travel

enemy6.name: Ayesha
enemy6.strengths: Genius level intellect, and acute genealogical perception
